{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 52865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然是后者", "timestamp": 1593250464, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "求求别这也阶级", "timestamp": 1593250505, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52868, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "求科普思源计划", "timestamp": 1593250510, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52873, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "选拔大于培养的因材施教计划都是这个样子", "timestamp": 1593250540, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把最好的资源给最优秀的学生，仅仅因为他们优秀。为什么优秀呢？大部分是因为运气好，既有高智商又有好的环境。所以因材施教等于按照运气分配资源，让运气好的更好", "timestamp": 1593250552, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52881, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“全面发展”的评价体系才是在制造阶级分化", "timestamp": 1593250589, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "糟糕 我连他们有什么资源都不知道", "timestamp": 1593250626, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把所有对立归结为阶级矛盾的人不是蠢就是坏", "timestamp": 1593250645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52902, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 那是什么对立呢", "timestamp": 1593250710, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52933, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因材施教就是因材施教，我觉得很好", "timestamp": 1593250969, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 52955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 倒不完全是因为运气好 我觉得这些计划的缺点在于 参加这些计划的人获得的资源太多 在学校里还有很多人除了上课之外没有得到任何资源 这种情况让他们更难以获得更多的资源 而参加计划的人得到资源以后能够去申请更多的资源 逐渐形成了两极分化 ", "timestamp": 1593251140, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 53011, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得这种是会两极分化，但是和阶级对立关系还真不大", "timestamp": 1593251568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 53128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "唉，马太效应是普遍规律啊", "timestamp": 1593252482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 53473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 嗯嗯嗯", "timestamp": 1593256573, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 81136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 8796, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学院级的因材施教计划很棒啊", "timestamp": 1593825730, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 8796, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "如何看待思源计划等因材施教计划，是因材施教还是在学生中制造阶级分化？", "timestamp": 1593250442, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782585, "url": "", "vote": {}}}